replies.body:
Well, actually - she can't. I checked her [bio](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/champion/akali/), and there's this;

> She was a prodigious fighter, and mastered the kama and kunai—a handheld sickle and throwing dagger. _Though she did not possess the magical abilities of many of her fellow acolytes_, she proved to all she was worthy of the title, in time allowing her mother to step down and help mentor the younger neophytes.

That said, lacking magical abilities doesn't mean she has no magical tools. Knowing Ionia, it wouldn't be too far-fetched to assume that the Kinkou would equip their best - especially the Fist of Shadow - with enchanted arms.
